isP1 = input.getBool(1) isP2 = input.getBool(2)
in1X = input.getNumber(3) in1Y = input.getNumber(4) in2X = input.getNumber(5) in2Y = input.getNumber(6) end
function onDraw() local scale = 0.1 local minusDisabled = false local plusDisabled = false
local barHeight = math.floor(h / 10) if barHeight < 6 then barHeight = 6 end
screen.drawMap(x, y, mapZoom)
setC(0,0,0) screen.drawLine(0, 31.5, 64, 31.5)
setC(0,0,0) screen.drawLine(32, 0, 32, 63.5) end
function setC(r,g,b,a) if a==nil then a=255 end screen.setColor(r,g,b,a)
end
